{"tid":835762,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"-【#Cult片】淺談何謂剝削電影《Exploitation film》","createTime":"2018-09-25T07:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T03:44:30.000Z","uid":212112,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28a2f3d4428aa2ac616813f7357dbd40bdfa8e04","tid":835762,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/150545_47b4ef772b76fce4206263da0964602d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F150545_47b4ef772b76fce4206263da0964602d.png&h=e07ff53d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大部分Cult片都包含剝削電影的元素，咁何謂剝削電影呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實將&quot;Exploitation&quot;一詞直接譯作「剝削」並不恰當，因為「剝削」一般人的理解是壓榨侵奪的意思，但在歐美電影界裡&quot;Exploitation&quot;有「廣告行銷」的意思，所以《Exploitation film》就是以「促銷題材」為主的電影。，而最能促鎖一齣電影的內容是最具有宣傳效果的，像是色情、暴力、血腥、靈異等，但Exploitation film往往又會將內容促銷得太過火，大大仰賴煽色情血腥，以及露骨、誇大其詞的內容描繪甚至不管製作水準，無視於電影自身的內在品質，所以Exploitation film往往被廣泛認為是品質低劣的電影產物。但即使如此，Exploitation film有時也能吸引世人關注、和膜拜追隨的Cult Film。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/150546_336f365f1fef824b1b8fa0bbbf2bc564.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F150546_336f365f1fef824b1b8fa0bbbf2bc564.gif&h=84320b06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而Exploitation film大致上可以再細分為以下幾大類：<br />\n黑幫摩托車電影 (Biker films)<br />\n黑人剝削電影 (Black exploitation)<br />\n食人族電影 (Cannibal films)<br />\n日本武士電影 (Chambara films)<br />\n意大利豔情驚悚電影 (Giallo films)<br />\n驚悚紀錄片 (Mondo films)<br />\n生態恐怖電影 (Nature run amok films)<br />\n納粹剝削電影 (Nazi exploitation)<br />\n強暴/復仇電影 (Rape / Revenge films)<br />\n性愛剝削電影 (Sex exploitation)<br />\n驚嚇剝削電影 (Shock exploitation)<br />\n汽車剝削電影（Carsploitation  exploitation）<br />\n女子監獄電影（Women in prison films）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/150548_6b56b3cc656c59f4682838304e31d6df.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F150548_6b56b3cc656c59f4682838304e31d6df.png&h=b1826356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實Exploitation film華人很常接觸到，因為上世紀七、八○年代香港流行的「鬼片」、「賭片」、「三級片」，甚至是「功夫片」，幾乎都是【Exploitation film】。而這些電影都是以譁眾取寵的方式，製造大量奇觀鏡頭，只求在短時間內賺取利潤，但電影架構常常是亂七八糟。<br />\n<br />\nBnLb18ghO9T/[/url]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/150550_0e8f8cf2544bdd4bccaffb37acef8de1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F150550_0e8f8cf2544bdd4bccaffb37acef8de1.png&h=0f25aaae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a61b7c926f689099c0dd360755bdd49ec523831","tid":835762,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:10:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/BnLb18ghO9T/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBnLb18ghO9T%2F&d=Mp8yynpZk4R88lIBgfKdKjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=dc540ab8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBnLb18ghO9T%2F&h=796e4912\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/p/BnLb18ghO9T/</a>"},{"pid":"d907a18211aaf4dd8c10f51653793bba9891328a","tid":835762,"uid":49228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:42:59.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a87578ba1a7773b533f8dcdf2718c80bbe48889","tid":835762,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T09:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871ed674fa3c9fbd1bf1977b1297e4a2f4bb8bb9","tid":835762,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0000206e13b86c446d6a040ca90781fd8babeb1c","tid":835762,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14